# kidney.epi 1.4 (2025-05-31)
* add calculation eGFR in adults by all available equations in a single function
* change internal service functions for checking biological plausibility boundaries
* the function for the Schwartz creatinine-based equation renamed to 'egfr.schwartz.cr' from 'egfr.schwartz', since cystatine C Schwartz equation egfr.schwartz.cys is introduced. 'egfr.schwartz' name is deprecated
* add several eGFR equations
* some minor bug fixes

# kidney.epi 1.3.0 (2025-03-31)
* add a set of functions for estimated glomerular filtration rate (eGFR) calculation
* change eGFR CKD-EPI function names due to availability of CKD-EPI 2009 and 2021 equations
* for KDPI calculation function extended KDPI mapping coefficients up to 2024 year 
* introduce additional service functions
* add ckd.data data set 
* rename data set ktx to ktx.data
* update vignettes

# kidney.epi 1.2.0 (2020-03-04)
* add a set of functions for estimated glomerular filtration rate (eGFR) calculation
* add OPTN mapping values for the years 2018 and 2014
* change parameter name from creatinineunits to creatinine_units in function ktx.kdpi.optn
* introduce additional service functions

# kidney.epi 1.1.0 (2018-09-10)
* introduce service functions
* add OPTN mapping values for the year 2017 to the internal dataframes in sysdata.rda
* add check of the user input for ktx.kdpi.optn function

# kidney.epi 1.0.0 (2018-06-19)
* first public release of the package
